      		:Description = "PDU Analog HK Telemetry. The PDU analog telemetry digitized by the HKT card and collected by the SBC Thermal Control Task. Packet Frequency is 1 in Hertz. Data is from the APID 1059 (Primary) or APID 1060 (Redundant) HK packets." ;
