      		:Description = "This DFCx_hk is a diagnostic packet (APID 1072, 1088, 1104) that contains some of the parameters normally part of APID 1254, 1264, 1274 (as sequence flag 01).   Also know as the PCE Altimetric Science Data Major Frame described in ICESat-2-MEB-SPEC-0875, section 5.13 Table 19. The data in the group are neither calibrated nor EU-converted, but preserved from ATL01 in order provided diagnostics for TOF processing." ;
